  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00613', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-6b8439ac', 'sub-public-health-specialist-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '我國長期照顧十年計畫2.0服務的對象除需經評估符合長照需要等級2級以上者，尚須符合', '["60 歲以上原住民", "65 歲以上老人", "50 歲以上失智者", "失能身 心障礙者"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4311540cfbeb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e5b303c5abe9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0804", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "衛生行政與管理", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00614', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-6b8439ac', 'sub-public-health-specialist-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關我國醫療機構分類，下列陳述何者錯誤？', '["醫療機構設置標準將醫療機構分為醫院、診所及其他醫療機構", "醫院依規模分為醫學中心、區域醫院及地區醫院", "醫院依主治醫師僱用方式分為開放性、閉鎖性及半開放性醫院", "依所有權分為公立、私立、醫療法人及法人附設機構"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4311540cfbeb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e5b303c5abe9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0804", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "衛生行政與管理", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00615', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-6b8439ac', 'sub-public-health-specialist-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '世界衛生組織於 2018 年揭櫫非傳染性疾病的主要風險，包含下列那些項目？①個人不健康', '["空氣污染", "身體活動不足", "不適當飲酒  ⑤不健康飲食", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4311540cfbeb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e5b303c5abe9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0804", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "衛生行政與管理", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00616', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-112-6b8439ac', 'sub-public-health-specialist-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '我國為促使嬰幼兒及兒童健康，推展諸多政策，下列陳述何者錯誤？', '["提供孕婦產前檢查12次", "補助新生兒先天性代謝異常疾病篩檢21項", "提供7歲以下兒童預防保健及衛教指導7次", "辦理低（含極低）出生體重兒居家照護試辦計畫"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:39+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4311540cfbeb", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e5b303c5abe9", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "108", "s": "0804", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "衛生行政與管理", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
